Program: Outlook
Title: Las Vegas Special
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbrsw
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
A profile of the city, the fastest growing city in the USA. Includes interviews with a cleaner, a topless dancer and a Folies Bergere showgirl, a look at the real CSI, and Troy Wade, chairman of the Nevada Test Site Historical Foundation talks about the nuclear weapons test site.